    "To test this observation on my class of masters students, I asked them to do the following with vectors from MUSE (which they had used previously): Some people are finding ChatGPT to be useful for documentation (e.g., as a replacement for Stack Overflow).",
    "Suppose I have a set of vectors from MUSE and I want to index them with annoy and/or faiss. 1.",
    "Find some documentation for how to do this. 2.",
    "If possible, find some examples. 3.",
    "Write a program that creates the index. 4."
  ],
